    <p><em>This is an automated email message, please do not reply!</em></p>
    
    <h1>New pilot has enrolled in the VATEUD PTD program!</h1>
    <p>
      Pilot name: <%= @pilot.name %><br/>
      Desired rating: <%= @pilot.rating.name %><br/>
      VATSIM ID: <%= @pilot.vatsimid %><br/>
